      "u": "(a) \"Exponentially\" = growing at a very fast, accelerating rate. Context clue: \"has grown… over the past decade\" combined with \"increasingly affordable\" suggests rapid, sustained growth.\n(b) \"Renewable energy\" (fixed combination = energy from natural sources like sun/wind); or \"ordinary households\" (typical homes); or \"increasingly affordable\" (gradually becoming cheaper). A collocation is a pair of words that naturally go together."
